The repository contains some TRNG circuits as samples, which are derived
from the following papers:
 - Naoki Fujieda, On the feasibility of TERO-based true random number
   generator on Xilinx FPGAs, 30th International Conference on Field-
   Programmable Logic and Applications (FPL 2020), pp. 103-108 (08/2020).
   ( https://github.com/nfproc/TC-TERO )
 - Naoki Fujieda and Shuichi Ichikawa: A Latch-latch Composition of
   Metastability-based True Random Number Generator for Xilinx FPGAs,
   IEICE Electronics Express, Vol. 15, No. 10, pp. 20180386:1-20180386:12
   (05/2018).

Copyright (C) 2018, 2020, 2021 Naoki FUJIEDA. All rights reserved.

The above license statement is applied to these circuits as well.
